# {{ EntityGraph.EntityName }}

## Summary

- **Steps**: {{ EntityGraph.Summary.TotalSteps }} total ({{ EntityGraph.Summary.SyncSteps }} sync, {{ EntityGraph.Summary.AsyncSteps }} async)
- **Handles**: {{ EntityGraph.Summary.MessageCountsMarkdown }}
- **API Calls**: {{ EntityGraph.Summary.TotalApiCalls }} across all steps
{{~ if EntityGraph.Summary.HasAffectedEntities ~}}
- **Reaches into**: {{ EntityGraph.Summary.AffectedEntitiesMarkdown }}
{{~ end ~}}
{{~ if EntityGraph.Summary.HasSelfRecursionWarnings ~}}

> ⚠️ **Possible self-recursion** — the step(s) below perform an API call matching their own trigger message + entity. If the call ends up targeting the same record without a depth/context guard, this can cause infinite recursion:
{{~ for step in EntityGraph.Summary.SelfRecursionWarnings ~}}
> - [`{{ step.Name }}`](#{{ step.AnchorId }}) ({{ step.SdkMessage }} · {{ step.StageName }})
{{~ end ~}}
{{~ else ~}}
- ✅ No self-recursion detected.
{{~ end ~}}

